452
00:45:35,700 --> 00:45:38,432
Zar je bilo teško
da je pristojno središ?

453
00:45:41,858 --> 00:45:44,046
Zar nemaš mirniju devojcicu?

454
00:45:51,184 --> 00:45:52,258
Možda ispred kuce.

455
00:45:57,814 --> 00:45:59,121
Chrissie, požuri!

456
00:46:02,824 --> 00:46:03,853
Veži ga, Chrissie.

457
00:46:06,934 --> 00:46:10,714
Eric, zaustavi je. Chrissie, stani,
