554
00:58:51,437 --> 00:58:57,520
Dadiljo McPhee?
Dadiljo McPhee?

555
01:00:02,827 --> 01:00:07,998
Zdravo, Simone, mogu li
da ti pomognem? - Kucao sam.

556
01:00:09,625 --> 01:00:11,922
